Package com.example.preemptiveoop.post

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ManageQuestionFragment
    The ManageQuestionFragment class is the fragment class that builds and manages the UI for the user to manage a question.
    PostArrayAdapter<T extends Post>
    The ExpArrayAdatper class is an ArrayAdapter class to be used by QuestionListActivity and ReplyListFragment to display a single item in the list.
    PostQuestionReplyFragment
    The PostQuestionReplyFragment class is the fragment class that builds and manages the UI for the user to post a question or a reply.
    QuestionListActivity
    The QuestionListActivity class is the activity class that builds and manages the UI for listing questions for an experiment.
    ReplyListFragment
    The ReplyListFragment class is the fragment class that builds and manages the UI for listing replies to a question.
